com.viaoa.web

Class OACombo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.web.OACombo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OAJspComponent, OAJspRequirementsInterface, OATableEditor, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OAComboBox, OAHtmlSelect

    public class OACombo
extends Object
implements OAJspComponent, OATableEditor, OAJspRequirementsInterface
    Controls html select+options bind to hub, property show/hide, that can be bound to property enabled, that can be bound to property ajax submit on change handle required validation recursive, displayed using indentation option to set the null description
    Author:
    vvia
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
